automatic calculator first being manchester university's small scale experimental machine ssem nicknamed baby which ran its first program on june this gave douglas perfect opportunity prove his findings by programming code for simple game where player can compete against computer — oxo jobs trinity college 1953–1957 elected prize fellow trinity college cambridge douglas spends year at university illinois computation laboratory assistant professor became junior bursar trinity college leeds leeds pegasus computer was installed autumn eldon chapel on woodhouse lane douglas set up computer laboratory university leeds was there that he first became interested application computers business problems pegasus holds especial place my affection being machine i installed central university machine disused chapel leeds — was known lucifer for leeds university computing installation ferranti our au pair girl from spain made beautiful little devilish doll which decorated machine — has probably disappeared by now june committee vice-chancellors principals set up working party explore creation national system for handling university admissions douglas was appointed member working party provide advice on use computers this system he had previously worked at leeds with ronald kay who was become ucca's general secretary on early primitive but successful attempt introduce computer methods into student registration procedures ceir entered commercial field technical director uk subsidiary c-e-i-r now scientific control systems leasco left ceir initiate european software interests leasco systems research ltd chairman douglas died sleep on april from pneumonia writings over papers have been published by professor douglas covering topics atomic physics crystallography solution differential equations computer design programming operational research shipbuilding oil chemical mining engineering transportation industries printing industry computers society inaugural lecture b c alexander sandy 